1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about senescent cells than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:09,600
Senescent cells are damaged cells that stop dividing but refuse to die.

3
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:13,600
They accumulate with age and contribute to aging and disease.

4
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:18,000
Studies show that targeting these cells may improve health and longevity.

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:20,400
But the science is still evolving.

6
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:22,000
More research is needed.

7
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,000
Follow for more insights into the science of our bodies.
